      "raw_text": "A movement is on foot to bring\nthe deputies Of the city treasurer's\nand comptroller's Offices under the\ncivil service. 1t Is proposed to\namend the city charter by the\nadoption of laws similar to Seat\ntie ordinances. The present hold\ners of position as deputies In the\ncity h<ll would not be compelled\nto take the civil service examina-\ntons, but would continue to hold\non until removed for cause or left\nof their own free will, The po-\nlice and fire departments are now\npractically under civil service. and\nit Is predicted that sooner or\nlater the same system for deputies\nwill prevail in this and all the\nlarge cities."
